dct_title_s: Map of the Turtle Bay Farm and its six subdivisions : accurately plotted from the field notes of surveys made in the year 1820 by John Randall Jr., City Surveyor, which field notes are recorded in Liber 147
dct_description_sm: Cadastral map. Also shows names of landholders, locations of old roads and buildings and original shoreline. Oriented with north to the upper right. Hand colored. Includes text.
